### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### FILE SERVICE (port 8089) — Test Requests
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### F1. Health check
GET http://localhost:8089/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### ─── UPLOAD: dùng curl trong Terminal (Alt+F12) ───
#
# Upload ảnh (tạo thumbnail tự động):
#   curl -v -X POST http://localhost:8089/api/files/upload \
#     -F "file=@tnguyen/test/test-image.png" \
#     -F "userId=nguyen" \
#     -F "channelId=1"
#
# Upload text file (không có thumbnail):
#   curl -v -X POST http://localhost:8089/api/files/upload \
#     -F "file=@tnguyen/test/test-file.txt;type=text/plain" \
#     -F "userId=nguyen" \
#     -F "channelId=1"
#
# Upload file quá lớn (expect 400/413):
#   dd if=/dev/zero of=tnguyen/test/test-big.bin bs=1M count=11
#   curl -v -X POST http://localhost:8089/api/files/upload \
#     -F "file=@tnguyen/test/test-big.bin" -F "userId=nguyen" -F "channelId=1"
#   rm tnguyen/test/test-big.bin

### F2. Xem metadata file id=1
GET http://localhost:8089/api/files/1/info
Accept: application/json

### F3. Download file gốc (trả binary)
GET http://localhost:8089/api/files/1

### F4. Download thumbnail (ảnh nhỏ 200x200)
GET http://localhost:8089/api/files/1/thumbnail

### F5. File không tồn tại → 404
GET http://localhost:8089/api/files/9999
Accept: application/json

### F6. Xóa file (owner)
DELETE http://localhost:8089/api/files/1?userId=nguyen

### F7. Xóa file (không phải owner → 403)
DELETE http://localhost:8089/api/files/2?userId=hacker

### ─── UPLOAD qua IntelliJ HTTP Client ───

### F8. Upload ảnh qua HTTP Client
POST http://localhost:8089/api/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-image.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./tnguyen/test/test-image.png
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

nguyen
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="channelId"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

### F9. Upload text inline qua HTTP Client
POST http://localhost:8089/api/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="readme.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Noi dung file text thu nghiem
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

nguyen
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="channelId"

2
--WebAppBoundary--
